action however i believe that the flag of the united states should 
never be the object of desecration 
flagburning is wrong protection of the flag a unique national 
symbol will in no way limit the opportunity nor the breadth of 
protest available in the exercise of free speech rights and i have 
the greatest respect for the supreme court and indeed for the 
justices who interpreted the constitution as they saw fit but i 
believe the importance of this issue compels me to call for a 
constitutional amendment 
support for the first amendment need not extend to desecration of 
the american flag and we are reviewing proposed language for a 
constitutional amendment we are beginning consultation with members 
of the united states congress who hold similar views and as 
president i will uphold our precious right to dissent but burning 
the flag goes too far and i want to see that matter remedied 
