this summit agreed monday to support in principle the linking of 
the british pound to a system that aligns the major eec currencies 
mrs thatcher rejects full monetary integration as surrendering 
to the eec national policymaking powers on budgetary and other 
financial matters 
mitterrand conference said he was very satisfied with the 
summit 
