late cc woodson craigs father bought the brownwood bulletin in 
1940 in 1959 craig woodson bought the company from his father 
boone newspapers inc an ownership and management company headed 
by board chairman james b boone jr of tuscaloosa ala manages 
the boone groups newspapers which are in alabama michigan 
mississippi new mexico and ohio 
